      "value": "<p>You use your Chakra to form a powerful electric aura around you, which crackles with energy. Each round, other creatures caught within the area during your turn suffers 8d4 electric damage. While active, you gain a +2 bonus to Reflex saves against electric effects, but suffer a -8 penalty to Hide and Move Silently checks, as well as taking a -4 penalty to saves against any Water effects.</p>\n\n\n\n",
